44701::$$$message_0397_0000_0000$$$::"...Tohsaka, promise me you won't get mad.[lr]::
44702::$$$message_0397_0000_0001$$$::But I'm thinking that...maybe I should..."[lr]::
44703::$$$message_0397_0000_0002$$$::"Take on Gilgamesh, right?[lr]::
44704::$$$message_0397_0000_0003$$$::...I'm surprised, so you did notice. The only thing that could counter Gilgamesh's Noble Phantasm...is Archer's magecraft."::
44705::$$$message_0397_0001_0000$$$::"Huh?"[lr]::
44706::$$$message_0397_0001_0001$$$::My jaw dropped.::
44707::$$$message_0397_0002_0000$$$::"What do you mean what? [wait canskip=0 time=500][chgfg textoff=0 time=300 storage=凛私服06a(中)]Don't tell me... You were thinking of something crazy like that without even realizing the most important part?"[lr]::
44708::$$$message_0397_0002_0001$$$::"Well...I wouldn't say that. I didn't have concrete evidence but I had a feeling that maybe I have the best chance against him..."::
44709::$$$message_0397_0003_0000$$$::"...Hmmm, I see. I'm not sure who gave you the idea, but you weren't wrong about that.[lr]::
44710::$$$message_0397_0003_0001$$$::What makes Gilgamesh the most powerful Servant is the number of his Noble Phantasms. But following the same line of thought, whoever possesses the same amount of Noble Phantasms could potentially go up against him."[lr]::
44711::$$$message_0397_0003_0002$$$::"...Same amount of Noble Phantasms."[lr]::
44712::$$$message_0397_0003_0003$$$::Basically, I just need to copy every single one of his weapons as soon as he unleashes them.::
44713::$$$message_0397_0004_0000$$$::"...That's right. I know he mocks you and calls you two fakers, but I'm sure that's just because he sees you two as threats. He has no choice but to admit that Heroic Spirit Emiya gets to fight him on the same ground."[lr]::
44714::$$$message_0397_0004_0001$$$::"..."[lr]::
44715::$$$message_0397_0004_0002$$$::That's true, but...::
44716::$$$message_0397_0005_0000$$$::"Maybe that's the case, but there's a limit.[lr]::
44717::$$$message_0397_0005_0001$$$::He can tell that as soon as I Project one of Archer's swords. There's no way I can Project fast enough and I don't have enough magical energy to do so."[lr]::
44718::$$$message_0397_0005_0002$$$::"That's only if your magecraft stays the same as before.[lr]::
44719::$$$message_0397_0005_0003$$$::But you do remember what Archer's Noble Phantasm is, right?[lr]::
44720::$$$message_0397_0005_0004$$$::That magecraft... As long as you can master that Reality Marble, you will have a chance against Gilgamesh."::
44721::$$$message_0397_0006_0000$$$::Tohsaka stares at me with high expectations.[lr]::
44722::$$$message_0397_0006_0001$$$::Unfortunately, I can't answer her expectations.::
44723::$$$message_0397_0007_0000$$$::"No way. Reality Marble is forbidden even amongst the most dangerous spells, right? Besides I don't know how to do it, and I don't even have a fraction of the magical energy needed when Archer created his world."::
44724::$$$message_0397_0008_0000$$$::"I know it'd be difficult.[lr]::
44725::$$$message_0397_0008_0001$$$::However, you should already know how to do it. That's because your magecraft all originates from it. Whether it's Strengthening or Projection, it's just a byproduct of your Reality Marble.[lr]::
44726::$$$message_0397_0008_0002$$$::As long as you have enough magical energy, I'm sure even you'll be surprised at how gears just fall into places by themselves."::
44727::$$$message_0397_0009_0000$$$::"Even if that's the case, it still doesn't change the impossible. I don't have the magical energy to put up or sustain the Reality Marble. [lr]::
44728::$$$message_0397_0009_0001$$$::I'm sure Archer spent his lifetime strengthening his Magic Circuits, but I don't have what he has..."::
44729::$$$message_0397_0010_0000$$$::"I understand.[lr]::
44730::$$$message_0397_0010_0001$$$::But Gilgamesh said so too, remember? A true mage would compensate for what's lacking in themselves from elsewhere."::
44731::$$$message_0397_0011_0000$$$::"Listen to me, I'm not skilled enough to try to siphon magical energy from other places, and I don't know how to store my magical energy into gems like you.[lr]::
44732::$$$message_0397_0011_0001$$$::...Wait, are you asking me to use those gems?"[lr]::
44733::$$$message_0397_0011_0002$$$::Of course, I don't think she'll agree to that seeing that I don't have any training in magecraft to be able to utilize those gems.::
44734::$$$message_0397_0012_0000$$$::"If that worked, I would've given you the gems already. Besides, only I'm capable of transferring those gems into energy so no, that wouldn't work.[lr]::
44735::$$$message_0397_0012_0001$$$::...But, maybe that's our only approach.[lr]::
44736::$$$message_0397_0012_0002$$$::There are a lot of steps we have to take in order to make someone else's magical energy your own, but I think that's the only option we're left with considering our situation..."::
44737::$$$message_0397_0013_0000$$$::"...Hey, Tohsaka. You mind sharing what's on your mind? I can't help if you don't tell me what's going on."[lr]::
44738::$$$message_0397_0013_0001$$$::"What? [wait canskip=0 time=600][chgfg textoff=0 time=300 storage=凛私服14a(中)]Th-there's no way I can tell you about something like that!::
44739::$$$message_0397_0014_0000$$$::...Hmmm.[lr]::
44740::$$$message_0397_0014_0001$$$::It seems she's thinking about something that's hard to tell me.::
44741::$$$message_0397_0015_0000$$$::"I-it's nothing.[lr]::
44742::$$$message_0397_0015_0001$$$::There are a couple of options, but I simply went through the process of elimination and got rid of the ones with a low chance of success..."[lr]::
44743::$$$message_0397_0015_0002$$$::"Is that so? Then does that mean you have a good plan now?"::
44744::$$$message_0397_0016_0000$$$::"Well...to be honest, this is a problem between me and you.[lr]::
44745::$$$message_0397_0016_0001$$$::There's a way to connect two mages' pools of magical energy together to make this work."::
44746::$$$message_0397_0017_0000$$$::"...So it would be like creating a path for the magical energy to pass through between us?"[lr]::
44747::$$$message_0397_0017_0001$$$::"Right. Even if you don't have enough magical energy for your Reality Marble, I do.[lr]::
44748::$$$message_0397_0017_0002$$$::You will use my magical energy to fight Gilgamesh, and Saber and I will destroy the Holy Grail during that time. I have Saber with me so we should be okay on our end even if I'm short on some magical energy."::
44749::$$$message_0397_0018_0000$$$::If I can use my Reality Marble to hold Gilgamesh back, without any other Servants and Masters, the Holy Grail is left wide open.[lr]::
44750::$$$message_0397_0018_0001$$$::Tohsaka being a mage and having Saber by her side, our chance of success is high enough.::
44751::$$$message_0397_0019_0000$$$::"...But that brings another issue, the hard part is the step before that. I don't know how to create a path for magical energy to pass through."[lr]::
44752::$$$message_0397_0019_0001$$$::"That much I'm aware. It'll be up to me to think of a way."::
44753::$$$message_0397_0020_0000$$$::Tohsaka is thinking of something.[lr]::
44754::$$$message_0397_0020_0001$$$::But she doesn't look optimistic about it.::
44755::$$$message_0397_0021_0000$$$::"About creating a path, there's only a handful of methods that are immediate and can allow magical energy to pass through.[lr]::
44756::$$$message_0397_0021_0001$$$::The most effective one would be to transplant our Magic Circuits into each other."::
44757::$$$message_0397_0022_0000$$$::...Transplant our Magic Circuits into each other?[lr]::
44758::$$$message_0397_0022_0001$$$::Magic Circuits are secondary pseudo-nerves that can be said to define a mage.[lr]::
44759::$$$message_0397_0022_0002$$$::Using od to exert influence on mana, the core mechanism of a mage.[lr]::
44760::$$$message_0397_0022_0003$$$::It's a "living inheritance" to make sure one's bloodline can have the foundation necessary to realize their family's great work when they've reached the pinnacle.[lr]::
44761::$$$message_0397_0022_0004$$$::You can say it's like one's blood and bone that strengthen as time goes on.::
44762::$$$message_0397_0023_0000$$$::"...Magic Circuits, like the ones in you and me?"[lr]::
44763::$$$message_0397_0023_0001$$$::"Yes. If we transplant our essences as mages to each other, it would guarantee a path.[lr]::
44764::$$$message_0397_0023_0002$$$::There's no easier way to transfer your magical energy to someone else when you have part of their circuit as your own."::
44765::$$$message_0397_0024_0000$$$::Her explanation is short and simple, yet contains a sense of guilt.[lr]::
44766::$$$message_0397_0024_0001$$$::...Of course it would. I can't even begin to imagine the consequences of doing something as crazy as transplanting your Magic Circuits into someone else.[lr]::
44767::$$$message_0397_0024_0002$$$::For a person to offer their own Magic Circuits to be transplanted, it also means they're giving up their integrity as a mage.[lr]::
44768::$$$message_0397_0024_0003$$$::But that makes this easier.::
44769::$$$message_0397_0025_0000$$$::"Okay, I will give you my Magic Circuits."[lr]::
44770::$$$message_0397_0025_0001$$$::"..."[lr]::
44771::$$$message_0397_0025_0002$$$::"Wh-what, Tohsaka?"[lr]::
44772::$$$message_0397_0025_0003$$$::"I'm happy that you'd think that, but that's meaningless."::
44773::$$$message_0397_0026_0000$$$::Right in my face.[lr]::
44774::$$$message_0397_0026_0001$$$::She just ends up throwing my resolve right back in my face.::
44775::$$$message_0397_0027_0000$$$::"Wh-why?"[lr]::
44776::$$$message_0397_0027_0001$$$::"Look. The reason why we're even talking about all this is so we can use your Reality Marble, right? Then why would we want to weaken your circuit?[lr]::
44777::$$$message_0397_0027_0002$$$::Using the Reality Marble is only possible when we fully exert all of our Magic Circuits."[lr]::
44778::$$$message_0397_0027_0003$$$::"..."::
44779::$$$message_0397_0028_0000$$$::...I see.[lr]::
44780::$$$message_0397_0028_0001$$$::I'm the one who will use the Reality Marble. I will only barely be able to create a fantasy big enough to corrode the world itself when I fully exert my Magic Circuits.[lr]::
44781::$$$message_0397_0028_0002$$$::If I were to transplant some of my Magic Circuits into Tohsaka to create a path, then I wouldn't have enough circuits to perform my magecraft, which would defeat the purpose.::
44782::$$$message_0397_0029_0000$$$::"Got it?[lr]::
44783::$$$message_0397_0029_0001$$$::That would be like spending all of this effort to just make us weaker, Shirou."[lr]::
44784::$$$message_0397_0029_0002$$$::"I'm sorry, I didn't think that far ahead."[lr]::
44785::$$$message_0397_0029_0003$$$::"It's ok, no need to apologize. I thought you would come up with something like that. I didn't expect you would say it so quickly though."::
44786::$$$message_0397_0030_0000$$$::"…So, we transplant your Magic Circuits into me?"[lr]::
44787::$$$message_0397_0030_0001$$$::But that also means...[lr]::
44788::$$$message_0397_0030_0002$$$::"...It's true that instead of transplanting your circuit into me, the reverse would better secure our chances.[lr]::
44789::$$$message_0397_0030_0003$$$::However, I'm the one performing the ritual for the transplant. Taking part of the circuit away while using it can't guarantee the stability of the ritual itself. [lr]::
44790::$$$message_0397_0030_0004$$$::My mind would be more at ease if this was standardized like the ritual we perform to form contracts with our familiars. But creating a path of magical energy between two mages is not something that happens everyday."::
44791::$$$message_0397_0031_0000$$$::"...So this could end up bad for the both of us?"[lr]::
44792::$$$message_0397_0031_0001$$$::"Right. I can't take your magical circuit and unfortunately me giving you my magical cirucit is also incorrect.[lr]::
44793::$$$message_0397_0031_0002$$$::And that's why..."[lr]::
44794::$$$message_0397_0031_0003$$$::"That's why...?"[lr]::
44795::$$$message_0397_0031_0004$$$::"I'm going to transplant my Magic Crest into you."::
44796::$$$message_0397_0032_0000$$$::Magic Crest.[lr]::
44797::$$$message_0397_0032_0001$$$::It records the secrets and hidden arts of a mage's family; it's their history.[lr]::
44798::$$$message_0397_0032_0002$$$::If Magic Circuits are the blood and bones of a mage, then one could say that the crest is their muscle.::
44799::$$$message_0397_0033_0000$$$::A Magic Crest is magecraft taking form.[lr]::
44800::$$$message_0397_0033_0001$$$::Through the life work of the mage leading the family in that generation, what was supposed to be formless is then given form. It is the proof of a mage's existence.[lr]::
44801::$$$message_0397_0033_0002$$$::Tohsaka having inherited her family's crest, she gets to enact the magecraft that this generation's family head created.::
44802::$$$message_0397_0034_0000$$$::"...Wait, but that means[line2]"[lr]::
44803::$$$message_0397_0034_0001$$$::"It's much easier to give a Magic Crest to someone. Unlike Magic Circuits, crests are meant to be given to others.[lr]::
44804::$$$message_0397_0034_0002$$$::...Well, while it doesn't define me as much as my Magic Circuits do, the crest is still created by the Tohsaka family, so it should suffice for our purpose."::
44805::$$$message_0397_0035_0000$$$::"...Are you sure?"[lr]::
44806::$$$message_0397_0035_0001$$$::"I'm sure. Well, the magecraft that was crystalized into the crest would probably be rendered useless, but at least I can turn that into a receiver for magical energy.[lr]::
44807::$$$message_0397_0035_0002$$$::Or are you talking about the success rate? Like is it possible to transplant the Magic Crest to someone outside my family's bloodline?"::
44808::$$$message_0397_0036_0000$$$::"...Yeah, that part worries me too, but..."[lr]::
44809::$$$message_0397_0036_0001$$$::"Don't worry, leave it to me. I will back you up, and we'll get that Holy Grail with you, me and Saber, the three of us.[lr]::
44810::$$$message_0397_0036_0002$$$::That's right, we already made up our minds. I will overcome my biggest failure with everything I've got."::
44811::$$$message_0397_0037_0000$$$::She asserts confidently with a bright smile.[lr]::
44812::$$$message_0397_0037_0001$$$::"..."[lr]::
44813::$$$message_0397_0037_0002$$$::There is nothing else that needs to be said.::
44814::$$$message_0397_0038_0000$$$::Removing her Magic Crest.[lr]::
44815::$$$message_0397_0038_0001$$$::That's the same as delaying her family's ultimate wish with her own hands.[lr]::
44816::$$$message_0397_0038_0002$$$::...I've seen that so many times.[lr]::
44817::$$$message_0397_0038_0003$$$::The fact that she could overcome that truth with a simple smile and with such determination is her strength, and I've seen it so many times.::
44818::$$$message_0397_0039_0000$$$::"Wh-what? Why are you smiling like that?[lr]::
44819::$$$message_0397_0039_0001$$$::I-is something weird on my face?"[lr]::
44820::$$$message_0397_0039_0002$$$::"What? ...Ummm. Right, it's the same when we went to the church. I don't know how to put this, but it's hard to know what to like about you."[lr]::
44821::$$$message_0397_0039_0003$$$::"...That's rude.[lr]::
44822::$$$message_0397_0039_0004$$$::That reminds me, was my face weird at that time?"::
44823::$$$message_0397_0040_0000$$$::The fated night when I summoned Saber.[lr]::
44824::$$$message_0397_0040_0001$$$::Tohsaka looked seriously worried about me, someone who is just her enemy, when I got sick at the church. I'll never forget how much that expression saved me. [lr]::
44825::$$$message_0397_0040_0002$$$::I can't say too much about others, but Tohsaka was a really nice person, probably nicer than anyone I've ever met.::
44826::$$$message_0397_0041_0000$$$::"Well yeah, it was weird.[lr]::
44827::$$$message_0397_0041_0001$$$::At the time I only thought of you as a goodie two-shoes at school, so I didn't think you would make a face like that."[lr]::
44828::$$$message_0397_0041_0002$$$::"...Whatever. That's right, I'm just a woman who's cold as the iceberg. Sorry I couldn't make it more obvious before."::
44829::$$$message_0397_0042_0000$$$::Yes, but I have been saved by her.[lr]::
44830::$$$message_0397_0042_0001$$$::She's kind yet realistic, and has the heart of steel who's willing to discard her weakness at a moment's notice.[lr]::
44831::$$$message_0397_0042_0002$$$::...She hides her hesitation and troubles in her heart, and always shows the elegant side of her to everyone, treading forward on her own path with grace.::
44832::$$$message_0397_0043_0000$$$::"And? It's fine what you think about me, but why are you still staring at me?"[lr]::
44833::$$$message_0397_0043_0001$$$::"What? Oh, I suppose I was captivated by you. I know it might be too late, but maybe I fell for you because of your charm."[lr]::
44834::$$$message_0397_0043_0002$$$::"...!"::
44835::$$$message_0397_0044_0000$$$::Then I can't lose.[lr]::
44836::$$$message_0397_0044_0001$$$::She's willing to transplant her Magical Crest to me without hesitation and regret. Then I must repay her kindness with my own trust.::
44837::$$$message_0397_0045_0000$$$::"[shock time=300 vmax=20 count=-4]Wh-what do you mean you f-fell for me? Now is not the time for that, but at least I can hear what else you want to say..."[lr]::
44838::$$$message_0397_0045_0001$$$::Tohsaka is readying herself.[lr]::
44839::$$$message_0397_0045_0002$$$::I'm glad. It seems she's prepared and has noticed my resolve.::
44840::$$$message_0397_0046_0000$$$::"Yeah, I understand. We're short on time so we probably shouldn't waste time on small talk, right?[lr]::
44841::$$$message_0397_0046_0001$$$::C'mon, let's start the transplant. Specifically, what am I supposed to do, Tohsaka?"[lr]::
44842::$$$message_0397_0046_0002$$$::"Huh?"[lr]::
44843::$$$message_0397_0046_0003$$$::Her mouth is wide open.[lr]::
44844::$$$message_0397_0046_0004$$$::...That's weird. Did I just say something funny?::
44845::$$$message_0397_0047_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
44846::$$$message_0397_0047_0001$$$::"What is it now? Did you just think of something we should be worried about?"[lr]::
44847::$$$message_0397_0047_0002$$$::For example, some kind of jinx that prevents us from performing the ritual at a certain time of day.[clfg textoff=0 time=10 storage=凛私服12c(中)]::
44848::$$$message_0397_0047_0003$$$::"...Nothing. I'm just having a headache right now.[lr]::
44849::$$$message_0397_0047_0004$$$::I thought I should be used to it by now, but I underestimated how bad you are with timing.[lr]::
44850::$$$message_0397_0047_0005$$$::...Hmph, it's fine since this is not the first time you've been like this. What you said... Well, it wasn't exactly bad so I'll let you off the hook for now."[lr]::
44851::$$$message_0397_0047_0006$$$::"???"::
44852::$$$message_0397_0048_0000$$$::She swings her body and turns away from me, [se storage=se512]and then she starts to take various items out of her bag.[lr]::
44853::$$$message_0397_0048_0001$$$::"Here, take this. Just think of it as a pain killer."[lr]::
44854::$$$message_0397_0048_0002$$$::"O-okay."[lr]::
44855::$$$message_0397_0048_0003$$$::I put the lozenge in my mouth.[lr]::
44856::$$$message_0397_0048_0004$$$::Tohsaka turns off the light in the room, and starts to draw some kind of pattern on the floor.::
44857::$$$message_0397_0049_0000$$$::About five minutes have passed.[lr]::
44858::$$$message_0397_0049_0001$$$::After the preparation is complete, Tohsaka sits down on the bed.::
44859::$$$message_0397_0050_0000$$$::"Okay, Tohsaka. What am I supposed to do now?"[lr]::
44860::$$$message_0397_0050_0001$$$::"..."[lr]::
44861::$$$message_0397_0050_0002$$$::It doesn't seem like she didn't hear my question.[lr]::
44862::$$$message_0397_0050_0003$$$::But Tohsaka is having this strange troubled look on her face.::
44863::$$$message_0397_0051_0000$$$::"What's going on? Is it something you can't tell me? I'm prepared for anything so it won't faze me unless it's something really surprising."[lr]::
44864::$$$message_0397_0051_0001$$$::This is what I meant by trust.[lr]::
44865::$$$message_0397_0051_0002$$$::Tohsaka nods her head.[lr]::
44866::$$$message_0397_0051_0003$$$::"...Fine, it is hard for me to say this but...[lr]::
44867::$$$message_0397_0051_0004$$$::Just take off your clothes."[lr]::
44868::$$$message_0397_0051_0005$$$::With nervousness in her tone, she issued me a command I'm not used to.::
44869::$$$message_0397_0051_0006$$$::"..."[lr]::
44870::$$$message_0397_0051_0007$$$::Let's assess the situation.[lr]::
44871::$$$message_0397_0051_0008$$$::The lights are off.[lr]::
44872::$$$message_0397_0051_0009$$$::Tohsaka is sitting on the bed with her head down, clearly nervous.[lr]::
44873::$$$message_0397_0051_0010$$$::...Why am I only realizing this now? Tohsaka's soft-looking body, and her supple legs dangling above the floor are all making her look very seductive.[lr]::
44874::$$$message_0397_0051_0011$$$::And...[lr]::
44875::$$$message_0397_0051_0012$$$::She's asking me to take off my clothes.::
44876::$$$message_0397_0052_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
44877::$$$message_0397_0052_0001$$$::"Hey you there! Don't get the wrong idea! I'm just telling you to take off your clothes![lr]::
44878::$$$message_0397_0052_0002$$$::I-I'm also going to take my clothes off so it's fair!"[lr]::
44879::$$$message_0397_0052_0003$$$::I took my weird fantasy back after she yelled at me.::
44880::$$$message_0397_0053_0000$$$::"...Wait? Are you...taking...your clothes off, too?"[lr]::
44881::$$$message_0397_0053_0001$$$::I don't know how else to interpret what she said other than taking it as exactly what it is.::
44882::$$$message_0397_0054_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
44883::$$$message_0397_0054_0001$$$::"I-I told you not to twist my words! I asked you to take off your clothes so we can sense each other's body warmth directly! Nothing else![lr]::
44884::$$$message_0397_0054_0002$$$::Listen! We must highly synchronize our senses in order to perform the Magic Crest transplant. In order for that to happen, we have to get rid of as much interference as possible."[lr]::
44885::$$$message_0397_0054_0003$$$::"O-Oh, ok. That makes sense."::
44886::$$$message_0397_0055_0000$$$::Of course.[lr]::
44887::$$$message_0397_0055_0001$$$::I'm not sure what transplanting a Magic Crest actually looks like, but from the sound of it, it could be similar to a medical transplant. I guess you wouldn't operate on a patient when they're fully clothed.[lr]::
44888::$$$message_0397_0055_0002$$$::"You could've told me that from the beginning... Ummm, I just need to take the top off, right?"[lr]::
44889::$$$message_0397_0055_0003$$$::"O-of course! I will throw the heater at you if you dare take your pants off!"::
44890::$$$message_0397_0056_0000$$$::It's scary thinking of what she might actually do.[lr]::
44891::$$$message_0397_0056_0001$$$::Taking off my top... I have had her take care of my injuries a few times already, but it still feels a little embarrassing.[lr]::
44892::$$$message_0397_0056_0002$$$::"..."[lr]::
44893::$$$message_0397_0056_0003$$$::I can hear Tohsaka taking a deep breath in the dark.::
44894::$$$message_0397_0057_0000$$$::"...Ok, now for the next step. Shirou, turn around."[lr]::
44895::$$$message_0397_0057_0001$$$::"Right, I forgot you have to take your clothes off, too."[lr]::
44896::$$$message_0397_0057_0002$$$::"..."[lr]::
44897::$$$message_0397_0057_0003$$$::No answer.[lr]::
44898::$$$message_0397_0057_0004$$$::Taking her silence as affirmation, I quietly turn around.::
44899::$$$message_0397_0058_0000$$$::"..."::
44900::$$$message_0397_0059_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
44901::$$$message_0397_0059_0001$$$::As I turn my back towards her, I take a deep breath to calm myself.[lr]::
44902::$$$message_0397_0059_0002$$$::I'm going to receive her Magic Crest, and create a path between us.[lr]::
44903::$$$message_0397_0059_0003$$$::Her magical energy will pass through it, and allow me to activate the Reality Marble in order to defeat that Servant.[lr]::
44904::$$$message_0397_0059_0004$$$::This is simply a process in this long and dangerous fight.[lr]::
44905::$$$message_0397_0059_0005$$$::I should be able to suppress unnecessary thoughts by just reaffirming that fact to myself.::
44906::$$$message_0397_0060_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
