45137::$$$message_0397_0123_0001$$$::Tohsaka, you're still there.[lr]::
45138::$$$message_0397_0123_0002$$$::That's a relief. I thought for sure I'd overslept and... Hmmm?::
45139::$$$message_0397_0124_0000$$$::...Am I imagining this or is she glaring at me?::
45140::$$$message_0397_0125_0000$$$::"...Ummm, Tohsaka? Was it successful?"[lr]::
45141::$$$message_0397_0125_0001$$$::"...Of course it was successful. It was a resounding success. It was so successful there's not even a slight trace of side effects. It was so perfectly done even Kirei would praise me with that devious face of his."[lr]::
45142::$$$message_0397_0125_0002$$$::"O-Oh, okay..."::
45143::$$$message_0397_0126_0000$$$::I-I'm sure that must be quite the achievement.[lr]::
45144::$$$message_0397_0126_0001$$$::But somehow, Tohsaka isn't proud about it and she doesn't feel like her usual arrogant self.[lr]::
45145::$$$message_0397_0126_0002$$$::Rather, she's angry.[lr]::
45146::$$$message_0397_0126_0003$$$::She's really, really angry.[lr]::
45147::$$$message_0397_0126_0004$$$::I can sense the tension between us... She's clearly sulking about something.::
45148::$$$message_0397_0127_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
45149::$$$message_0397_0127_0001$$$::...I don't know why, but it seems something has gone wrong.[lr]::
45150::$$$message_0397_0127_0002$$$::I feel like I need to read her mind immediately and calm her down, but I'm such a bad pupil, I'm not able to think of any reason as to why Tohsaka would be angry.::
45151::$$$message_0397_0128_0000$$$::"...Toh..."[lr]::
45152::$$$message_0397_0128_0001$$$::This persistent pain in my left arm.[lr]::
45153::$$$message_0397_0128_0002$$$::A strange feeling that's like a combination of sharp pain from deep cuts and stinging pain from being burnt.::
45154::$$$message_0397_0129_0000$$$::"Whoa..."[lr]::
45155::$$$message_0397_0129_0001$$$::Without a doubt.[lr]::
45156::$$$message_0397_0129_0002$$$::A streak of an elaborately designed seal is branded on my left arm.[lr]::
45157::$$$message_0397_0129_0003$$$::It looks like Tohsaka's Magic Crest, and it emits a faint blue light.::
45158::$$$message_0397_0130_0000$$$::"Tohsaka, is this...?"[lr]::
45159::$$$message_0397_0130_0001$$$::"Yes, this is the Magic Crest I transplanted. It already became part of your circuit and any traces of its original magecraft is nowhere to be seen."[lr]::
45160::$$$message_0397_0130_0002$$$::"I see... Well, this sure is something. I thought it would hurt but it doesn't really hurt at all. If anything my arm only feels a bit more heavy than before."::
45161::$$$message_0397_0131_0000$$$::"You'll get used to it soon. Since its sole purpose is to connect our magical energies together, it shouldn't have any effect on the human body.[lr]::
45162::$$$message_0397_0131_0001$$$::The Magic Crest...or rather, the circuit will slowly assimilate into your body, and you won't even feel a thing in about half a year."[lr]::
45163::$$$message_0397_0131_0002$$$::"Is that so? Then this means..."::
45164::$$$message_0397_0132_0000$$$::"The transplant is complete. It's basically a one-way path from me to you, so it's not possible for you to send your magical energy to me. All I can do for you now is to send you my magical energy.[lr]::
45165::$$$message_0397_0132_0001$$$::It's all up to you now. We have secured the magical energy necessary to create the Reality Marble, all that's left is[line2]"::
45166::$$$message_0397_0133_0000$$$::My problem.[lr]::
45167::$$$message_0397_0133_0001$$$::All I need to do is fully activate my Magic Circuit and successfully create the Reality Marble.::
45168::$$$message_0397_0134_0000$$$::"...You're right. Thank you, Tohsaka. I'll make good use of your Magic Crest."[lr]::
45169::$$$message_0397_0134_0001$$$::"You better. Also don't expect me to apologize. You don't just owe me one, you owe me a trillion and it's a lifetime worth of debt."[lr]::
45170::$$$message_0397_0134_0002$$$::"Hahaha, you're right about that.[lr]::
45171::$$$message_0397_0134_0003$$$::Oh. Why were you so angry just now?"::
45172::$$$message_0397_0135_0000$$$::"...You saw it, right?"[lr]::
45173::$$$message_0397_0135_0001$$$::"Eh?"[lr]::
45174::$$$message_0397_0135_0002$$$::What did I see exactly?[lr]::
45175::$$$message_0397_0135_0003$$$::...D-don't tell me that when I thought I blanked out during the ritual, my body actually acted on its own and did something to Tohsaka!?::
45176::$$$message_0397_0136_0000$$$::"W-wait a minute, did I do something!?"[lr]::
45177::$$$message_0397_0136_0001$$$::"Don't act so innocent! You saw it, you animal!"[lr]::
45178::$$$message_0397_0136_0002$$$::"A-[shock time=400 vmax=30 count=-3]animal!?"[lr]::
45179::$$$message_0397_0136_0003$$$::Not possible! Did I actually do something to her that was so rough that she would use that word to describe me!?[lr]::
45180::$$$message_0397_0136_0004$$$::Wait, there's no way that happened. I mean, the bed is tidy, and besides, I wouldn't be alive if anything like that happened.::
45181::$$$message_0397_0137_0000$$$::"N-now I remember. First and foremost, my eyes weren't functioning during the ritual so I really couldn't see anything other than what looked like the Magic Circuit and[line2]"::
45182::$$$message_0397_0138_0000$$$::Ah.[lr]::
45183::$$$message_0397_0138_0001$$$::...Maybe that's what Tohsaka was talking about?[lr]::
45184::$$$message_0397_0138_0002$$$::An illusion I saw for a brief moment.[lr]::
45185::$$$message_0397_0138_0003$$$::In the state where we were sharing our senses due to the synchronization, it's possible that we could see imagery from each other's mind.[lr]::
45186::$$$message_0397_0138_0004$$$::It wouldn't be much different than when I saw Saber's dream or Heroic Spirit Emiya's dream.::
45187::$$$message_0397_0139_0000$$$::It all makes sense now.[lr]::
45188::$$$message_0397_0139_0001$$$::If this is the case, then the only thing I saw that she would care about is that scene taking place at a school yard during sunset, something that I haven't seen in my other dreams.::
45189::$$$message_0397_0140_0000$$$::"...I got it."[lr]::
45190::$$$message_0397_0140_0001$$$::"It must be that. Tohsaka, you've been having a weird dream, right?[lr]::
45191::$$$message_0397_0140_0002$$$::At some school yard somewhere, you kept looking at an idiot who wouldn't give up on high jumping until sunset. What was that abou[line2][wsay canskip=1], [playstop time=200 nowait=1][se storage=se605][dash textoff=0 mx=0 opacity=255 layer=base irot=-0.0 cx=400 imag=3.3 time=200 cy=301 mag=1.2 my=0 storage=m02タイガーぱんち rot=-0.0 accel=0][quake time=1500 vmax=30 hmax=10][wdash canskip=0][say storage=rin1508s_shi_0691]whoa!"::
45192::$$$message_0397_0141_0000$$$::I was hit by a pillow before I could finish my sentence.[lr]::
45193::$$$message_0397_0141_0001$$$::It was a swift and powerful swing.[lr]::
45194::$$$message_0397_0141_0002$$$::A critical strike even Saber and Fuji-nee would be proud of!::
45195::$$$message_0397_0142_0000$$$::"Guh...hah..."[lr]::
45196::$$$message_0397_0142_0001$$$::There's another problem.[lr]::
45197::$$$message_0397_0142_0002$$$::It's the fact that a normal, soft pillow can have the impact and damage as if it was filled with water or something.::
45198::$$$message_0397_0143_0000$$$::"...Tohsaka, what are you..!"[lr]::
45199::$$$message_0397_0143_0001$$$::"Shut up shut up SHUT UP!"::
45200::$$$message_0397_0144_0000$$$::She keeps on hitting me with the pillow.[lr]::
45201::$$$message_0397_0144_0001$$$::Still looking like she did when she started the ritual, Tohsaka continues her assault with the pillow.::
45202::$$$message_0397_0145_0000$$$::"Ouch, ouch! Did you fuse some magical energy into that thing!?[lr]::
45203::$$$message_0397_0145_0001$$$::Would you just quit it and tell me what is up with you!?"[lr]::
45204::$$$message_0397_0145_0002$$$::"Shut up you animal! How dare you peek at someone's secret and just act like nothing happened!"[lr]::
45205::$$$message_0397_0145_0003$$$::"Ow...ahh...w-wait a minute, that's a secret to you!?"::
45206::$$$message_0397_0146_0000$$$::When I was surprised by her answer, she saw the opening and hit me in the face.[lr]::
45207::$$$message_0397_0146_0001$$$::"Oh."[lr]::
45208::$$$message_0397_0146_0002$$$::"Eek."[lr]::
45209::$$$message_0397_0146_0003$$$::That was a swift and powerful pillow uppercut.::
45210::$$$message_0397_0147_0000$$$::Maybe it's also the exhaustion from the transplant, but I'm haphazardly knocked down again.[lr]::
45211::$$$message_0397_0147_0001$$$::Tohsaka must still be angry because she grabs me by the back of the neck and starts dragging me across the floor.::
45212::$$$message_0397_0148_0000$$$::"...Hmph. Fine, you just remember this moment. One day, I will peek at your embarrassing memories and it will be too late to beg me for forgiveness."[lr]::
45213::$$$message_0397_0148_0001$$$::"Please forgive me... Wait, what are you doing..."::
45214::$$$message_0397_0149_0000$$$::She won't hear me out at all.[lr]::
45215::$$$message_0397_0149_0001$$$::She grabs the back of my neck and throws me out of her room.::
45216::$$$message_0397_0150_0000$$$::"Mr. Emiya? Just so you know, a girl has a lot to do to get ready, so would you return to your room now?"[lr]::
45217::$$$message_0397_0150_0001$$$::With that evil grin of hers... Tohsaka slams the door.[lr]::
45218::$$$message_0397_0150_0002$$$::...Thrown out into the hallway looking like this, I blankly look up at the door.::
45219::$$$message_0397_0151_0000$$$::"...Don't be ridiculous. Guys have lots of stuff to do too."[lr]::
45220::$$$message_0397_0151_0001$$$::I hold my dizzy head and get up.[lr]::
45221::$$$message_0397_0151_0002$$$::I thought of saying something back to Tohsaka on the other side of the door, but I decide not to.[lr]::
45222::$$$message_0397_0151_0003$$$::I wasn't able to ask Tohsaka what that scene I saw meant to her.::
45223::$$$message_0397_0152_0000$$$::"...Well. If she's that mad about it, it must have some special meaning to her."[lr]::
45224::$$$message_0397_0152_0001$$$::Muttering silly stuff like that to myself, I go back to my room.::
45225::$$$message_0397_0153_0000$$$::It was probably just an excuse for Tohsaka to kick me out, but it's true that there's no time.[lr]::
45226::$$$message_0397_0153_0001$$$::The date has already changed.[lr]::
45227::$$$message_0397_0153_0002$$$::There's probably less than an hour left before we head to the temple.::
45228::$$$message_0397_0154_0000$$$::"Hm... Yeah, this is..."[lr]::
45229::$$$message_0397_0154_0001$$$::I close my eyes and feel the magical energy from Tohsaka pouring into me.[lr]::
45230::$$$message_0397_0154_0002$$$::Tohsaka isn't consciously supplying me, yet it's filling my body up.::
45231::$$$message_0397_0155_0000$$$::If my maximum magical energy capacity is twenty or thirty units, then she always has 500 units of magical energy.[lr]::
45232::$$$message_0397_0155_0001$$$::...I'm sure it would take years to stock up, but her maximum capacity might reach 1000 units if someone supplied her.::
45233::$$$message_0397_0156_0000$$$::"...I'm surprised. She really is amazing."[lr]::
45234::$$$message_0397_0156_0001$$$::That reconfirms it. Or rather, I finally realize it now.[lr]::
45235::$$$message_0397_0156_0002$$$::Well, she's depleted now, and mages usually only keep about eighty percent of their magical energy, so Tohsaka's magical energy is about 400 units right now.::
45236::$$$message_0397_0157_0000$$$::But, that's still a massive amount of magical energy.[lr]::
45237::$$$message_0397_0157_0001$$$::I use about two units of magical energy to use Strengthening magecraft once.[lr]::
45238::$$$message_0397_0157_0002$$$::To use Projection once, I use about five units of magical energy on average.[lr]::
45239::$$$message_0397_0157_0003$$$::Using that example, the Projection that I can use only six times at most could be used thirty or even sixty times with the help of Tohsaka.::
45240::$$$message_0397_0158_0000$$$::"...Well, a cheap vehicle will overheat no matter how much fuel there is..."[lr]::
45241::$$$message_0397_0158_0001$$$::But it has still tremendously increased my power.[lr]::
45242::$$$message_0397_0158_0002$$$::I might even have a chance of winning against that King of Heroes like this.::
45243::$$$message_0397_0159_0000$$$::All that's left is...[lr]::
45244::$$$message_0397_0159_0001$$$::"...There's one more hour. I should rest my body until then."[lr]::
45245::$$$message_0397_0159_0002$$$::I'll rest my body and regain my mental and physical strength for the final battle at Ryudou Temple.[lr]::
45246::$$$message_0397_0159_0003$$$::...Everything is set.[lr]::
45247::$$$message_0397_0159_0004$$$::I'll face the last night with a fully prepared body for Tohsaka's sake too since she gave me her Magic Crest and opened up to me...Jyk"